#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:38
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— 25% speed increase on all shots"
msgstr "— aumento della velocità del 25% su tutti i colpi"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro.html.heex:73
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— 3-minute race in permanent darkness with fog bursts"
msgstr "— gara di 3 minuti nelle tenebre permanenti con esplosioni di nebbia"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid.html.heex:65
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— 5 sections, narrow river, faster mine recharge"
msgstr "— 5 sezioni, fiume stretto, ricarica rapida della miniera"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:44
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— 60% success rate (same as Classic)"
msgstr "— tasso di successo del 60% (stesso come classico)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro.html.heex:79
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— 90-second daylight sprint, no weather, no fuel drain"
msgstr ""
"— 90 secondi di luce del giorno, nessun tempo, nessun scarico del carburante"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw.html.heex:63
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— A moving stagecoach blocks shots with unpredictable timing"
msgstr "— Uno stagecoach commovente blocca i colpi con tempi imprevedibili"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_escape.html.heex:57
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— A stun at high speeds means the avalanche catches up instantly. One "
"collision can end your run."
msgstr ""
"— Uno stallone ad alta velocità significa che la valanga raggiunge "
"immediatamente. Una collisione può finire la corsa."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_night.html.heex:55
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— AI cars appear as colored dots at the edge of your vision. React to dot "
"colors to predict their lane."
msgstr ""
"— le auto dell'IA appaiono come punti colorati al bordo della vostra "
"visione. Reagisci ai colori del punto per prevedere la loro corsia."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro.html.heex:23
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_night.html.heex:23
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_sprint.html.heex:23
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_blitz.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_pacifist.html.heex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Accelerate"
msgstr "— Accelerare"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro.html.heex:32
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_night.html.heex:32
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_sprint.html.heex:32
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Activate turbo boost"
msgstr "— Attivare turbo boost"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_nml.html.heex:43
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Advancing gives you faster bullet travel time but also means less time to "
"dodge. Find your sweet spot."
msgstr ""
"— L'avanzamento ti dà il tempo di viaggio più veloce del proiettile, ma "
"significa anche meno tempo per schivare. Trova il tuo punto debole."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_blitz.html.heex:51
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Aliens descend faster in Blitz. Focus on the lowest rows to buy yourself "
"time."
msgstr ""
"— Gli alieni discendono più velocemente in Blitz. Concentrati sulle righe "
"più basse per guadagnare tempo."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_pong.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_light_trails.html.heex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Alternative controls"
msgstr "— Controlli alternativi"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_blizzard.html.heex:62
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— At 0.5°/second, you have about 2 minutes. Don't panic but don't dawdle "
"either."
msgstr ""
"— A 0.5° <ph0> </ph0>, avete circa 2 minuti. Non farti prendere dal panico, "
"ma non mollare."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_blitz.html.heex:58
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— At combo 4+, armored drops appear. These take 2 hits and can clog your "
"opponent's screen."
msgstr ""
"— A combo 4+, appaiono gocce corazzate. Questi prendono 2 colpi e possono "
"intasare lo schermo del tuo avversario."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:92
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Bonus collectible between rows (200 points)"
msgstr "— Bonus collezionabile tra righe (200 punti)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro.html.heex:29
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_night.html.heex:29
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_sprint.html.heex:29
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Brake"
msgstr "— Freno"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_pacifist.html.heex:41
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Bridges give the highest point rewards. Never miss a bridge kill."
msgstr ""
"— I ponti danno le più alte ricompense. Non perdere mai un ponte ucciso."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_ricochet.html.heex:51
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Bullets always bounce at matching angles. Position yourself so the "
"ricochet lands where your opponent tends to stand."
msgstr ""
"— I proiettili rimbalzano sempre ad angoli di corrispondenza. Posizionati in"
" modo che il ricochet atterra dove il tuo avversario tende a stare."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw.html.heex:54
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Bullets fire at 30-degree angles and bounce once off ceiling/floor"
msgstr ""
"— Bullets fuoco ad angolo di 30 gradi e rimbalzo una volta spento soffitto"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_warlords.html.heex:19
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Catch fireball on shield contact"
msgstr "— Prendere la palla di fuoco sul contatto dello scudo"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_night.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_sprint.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Change lane left"
msgstr "— Cambiare la corsia sinistra"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_night.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_sprint.html.heex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Change lane right"
msgstr "— Cambiare la linea destra"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis.html.heex:64
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Classic: full set with tiebreak at 6-6"
msgstr "— Classico: set completo con tiebreak a 6-6"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_coop.html.heex:54
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Clearing aliens from the sides slows horizontal movement for the entire "
"wave."
msgstr ""
"— Eliminare gli alieni dai lati rallenta il movimento orizzontale per "
"l'intera onda."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_clean.html.heex:45
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Courses repeat. In best-of-3, the third round favors the player who "
"learned the layout."
msgstr ""
"— I corsi si ripetono. Nel migliore dei 3, il terzo round favorisce il "
"giocatore che ha imparato il layout."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid.html.heex:20
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_blitz.html.heex:20
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_pacifist.html.heex:20
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Decelerate"
msgstr "— Decelerato"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_blitz.html.heex:57
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Decelerate in narrow sections. One wrong move at high speed means instant "
"death on the banks."
msgstr ""
"— Scelta in sezioni strette. Una mossa sbagliata ad alta velocità significa "
"morte istantanea sulle banche."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing.html.heex:66
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Dense ice patches, fast avalanche, narrow gates"
msgstr "— Pezze di ghiaccio denso, valanga veloce, cancelli stretti"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_sprint.html.heex:72
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Don't waste time recovering from crashes. Stay focused from second one."
msgstr ""
"— Non sprecare tempo recuperando da crash. Resta concentrato dal secondo."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid.html.heex:29
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_blitz.html.heex:29
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Drop mine"
msgstr "— Mina di goccia"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_clean.html.heex:31
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Each gate saves 2 seconds. Over a full run, gates make the difference "
"between winning and losing."
msgstr ""
"— Ogni cancello salva 2 secondi. Durante una corsa completa, i cancelli "
"fanno la differenza tra vincere e perdere."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_coop.html.heex:47
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Each player takes a side. Overlapping coverage wastes shots and leaves "
"gaps."
msgstr ""
"— Ogni giocatore prende un lato. Sovrapposizione dei rifiuti di copertura "
"colpi e lascia vuoti."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis.html.heex:76
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Each point wins a game, first to 6"
msgstr "— Ogni punto vince un gioco, prima a 6"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_coop.html.heex:68
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Earlier waves are easier. Play conservatively to have lives for waves "
"8-10."
msgstr ""
"— Le prime onde sono più facili. Giocare conservativamente per avere vite "
"per onde 8-10."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_peaceful.html.heex:62
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Enemies still escalate. In later rounds, focus on survival over speed."
msgstr ""
"— I nemici sono ancora in aumento. Nei round successivi, concentrati sulla "
"sopravvivenza sulla velocità."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_peaceful.html.heex:48
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Even though stealing is off, being on the same row as your opponent means "
"fewer blocks for you."
msgstr ""
"— Anche se rubare è spento, essere sulla stessa fila del vostro avversario "
"significa meno blocchi per voi."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_quick.html.heex:53
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Even when behind in a game, fighting to deuce gives you a chance. Never "
"give up a game easily."
msgstr ""
"— Anche quando dietro in un gioco, combattere per deuce ti dà una "
"possibilità. Mai rinunciare a un gioco facilmente."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_sudden.html.heex:40
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Every single rally decides a game. Stay focused for every point."
msgstr ""
"— Ogni singolo rally decide un gioco. Resta concentrato per ogni punto."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:76
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Fast pucks that hit the corners of the goal are nearly impossible to save."
msgstr ""
"— Puck veloci che hanno colpito gli angoli dell'obiettivo sono quasi "
"impossibili da salvare."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_nml.html.heex:15
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_ricochet.html.heex:19
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_stagecoach.html.heex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Fire (one bullet at a time)"
msgstr "— Fuoco (un proiettile alla volta)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_debris_field.html.heex:29
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_gravity_well.html.heex:29
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders.html.heex:23
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_blitz.html.heex:23
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_coop.html.heex:23
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid.html.heex:26
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_blitz.html.heex:26
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_pacifist.html.heex:26
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_pixel_tanks.html.heex:20
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_star_duel.html.heex:29
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Fire missile"
msgstr "— missili antincendio"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis.html.heex:70
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_p2p_games.html.heex:127
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— First to 3 games wins"
msgstr "— Prima a 3 vittorie di giochi"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:80
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Fly between rows, danger during jumps (from round 3)"
msgstr "— Volare tra le righe, pericolo durante i salti (dal giro 3)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_escape.html.heex:64
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Focus on the obstacles ahead, not the death wall behind you. Trust your "
"speed and dodge forward."
msgstr ""
"— Concentratevi sugli ostacoli avanti, non sulla parete di morte dietro di "
"voi. Fidatevi della vostra velocità e schivate in avanti."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_night.html.heex:62
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Fog bursts reduce visibility to nearly zero. Slow down when fog hits and "
"stay centered."
msgstr ""
"— Le esplosioni di nebbia riducono la visibilità a quasi zero. Rallenta "
"quando la nebbia colpisce e resta al centro."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:50
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Free puck gradually slows down on the ice"
msgstr "— Puck libero gradualmente rallenta sul ghiaccio"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro.html.heex:67
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Full Classic Duel: 3 days with weather cycle"
msgstr "— Full Classic Duel: 3 giorni con ciclo meteo"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders.html.heex:62
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Full rules: alien drops, combos, 10 waves"
msgstr "— Regole complete: gocce aliene, combo, 10 onde"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid.html.heex:53
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Full rules: mines, fuel competition, 10 sections"
msgstr "— Regole complete: miniere, concorrenza dei combustibili, 10 sezioni"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_nml.html.heex:64
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Half-measures get you killed. Either push hard or stay back and react."
msgstr ""
"- Le meta' misure ti fanno uccidere. O spingere duro o rimanere indietro e "
"reagire."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_coop.html.heex:61
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— If one cannon goes down, the other faces the full wave alone. Keep each "
"other alive."
msgstr ""
"— Se un cannone va giù, l'altro affronta l'onda piena da solo. Tenetevi "
"vivi."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:56
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— If the puck stops for 5 seconds, a face-off is called"
msgstr "— Se il puck si ferma per 5 secondi, si chiama un face-off"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:76
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— If tied at the end, the next goal wins. Stay composed under pressure."
msgstr ""
"— Se legato alla fine, il prossimo obiettivo vince. Soggiorno composto sotto"
" pressione."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_blitz.html.heex:65
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— In Blitz, volume of kills matters more than perfect accuracy. Keep firing."
msgstr ""
"— In Blitz, il volume di uccisione conta più della precisione perfetta. "
"Continua a sparare."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_quick.html.heex:46
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— In a short match, holding serve is critical. Aim for the corners on your "
"service games."
msgstr ""
"— In una breve partita, tenere il servizio è fondamentale. Mira agli angoli "
"dei tuoi giochi di servizio."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing.html.heex:39
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Infinite descent, ever-accelerating avalanche, last skier standing wins"
msgstr ""
"— Discesa infinita, valanga sempre accelerata, vince l'ultimo sciatore in "
"piedi"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders.html.heex:74
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Instant drops, easier combos, 5 waves"
msgstr "— Gocce istantanee, pettine più facili, 5 onde"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_blizzard.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_peaceful.html.heex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Jump to row above"
msgstr "— Salta alla riga sopra"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_blizzard.html.heex:23
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_peaceful.html.heex:23
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Jump to row below"
msgstr "— Salta alla riga qui sotto"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Jump to the row above (toward shore)"
msgstr "— Salto alla fila sopra (verso la riva)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:23
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Jump to the row below (toward water)"
msgstr "— Salto alla riga sottostante (acqua verso l'alto)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_night.html.heex:76
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Keep a mental tally. If you're ahead, play safe. If behind, take risks in "
"the final minute."
msgstr ""
"- Tenere un tally mentale. Se sei avanti, gioca al sicuro. Se dietro, rischi"
" nell'ultimo minuto."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_warlords.html.heex:25
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Launch fireball toward opponent"
msgstr "— Avviare la palla di fuoco verso l'avversario"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:38
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Launches puck at 2× your movement speed in your facing direction"
msgstr ""
"— Lancia puck a 2× la velocità di movimento nella vostra direzione di fronte"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_stagecoach.html.heex:59
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Match your vertical position to stay in the gap the stagecoach leaves "
"behind as it moves."
msgstr ""
"— Abbina la tua posizione verticale per rimanere nel vuoto il gioco di scena"
" lascia dietro mentre si muove."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing.html.heex:60
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— More rocks, faster avalanche, medium gates"
msgstr "— Più rocce, valanga più veloce, cancelli medio"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_boxing.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move boxer (8 directions)"
msgstr "— Spostare boxer (8 direzioni)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_blitz.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_coop.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move cannon left"
msgstr "— Spostare il cannone sinistra"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_blitz.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_coop.html.heex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move cannon right"
msgstr "— Spostare destra cannone"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_nml.html.heex:50
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Move forward to draw a shot, then dodge it while your opponent reloads."
msgstr ""
"— Spostatevi in avanti per disegnare un colpo, poi schivarlo mentre il "
"vostro avversario ricarica."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move gunslinger (vertical; horizontal in No Man's Land)"
msgstr "— Spostare il pistolero (verticale; orizzontale in No Man's Land)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_stagecoach.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move gunslinger vertically"
msgstr "— Spostare il cannone verticalmente"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_nml.html.heex:12
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move gunslinger vertically and horizontally within your half"
msgstr ""
"— Spostare il cannone verticalmente e orizzontalmente nella vostra metà"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move in 8 directions"
msgstr "— Spostare in 8 direzioni"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_blizzard.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_peaceful.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move left/right"
msgstr "— Spostare la sinistra"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move left/right on blocks or shore"
msgstr "— Spostare a sinistra l'identificativo/ph0> su blocchi o riva"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_block_breakers.html.heex:13
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_pong.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move paddle"
msgstr "— Spostare la paddle"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_quick.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_sudden.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move player"
msgstr "— Giocatore mobile"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_warlords.html.heex:13
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move shield vertically"
msgstr "— Spostare lo schermo verticalmente"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_ricochet.html.heex:13
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Move vertically and set aim direction (last pressed determines angle)"
msgstr ""
"— Spostare verticalmente e impostare la direzione dell'obiettivo (l'ultima "
"pressione determina l'angolo)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:32
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Neutral. Step on it to claim it (+1 igloo piece)"
msgstr "— Neutral. Passo su di esso per rivendicarlo (+1 pezzo igloo)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing.html.heex:48
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— No avalanche, no items, pure time trial racing"
msgstr "— Nessuna valanga, nessun elemento, prova di tempo puro"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:110
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_p2p_games.html.heex:203
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— No block stealing, pure construction race"
msgstr "— Nessun blocco rubare, pura gara di costruzione"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_sprint.html.heex:51
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— No fuel means no reason to brake unless you're about to crash. Keep the "
"pedal down."
msgstr ""
"— Nessun carburante significa nessun motivo per frenare a meno che non si "
"sta per schiantarsi. Abbassa il pedale."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid.html.heex:59
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_p2p_games.html.heex:163
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— No mines, pure skill competition"
msgstr "— Nessuna miniera, pura concorrenza di abilità"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw.html.heex:69
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— No obstacle, but players can advance horizontally within their half"
msgstr ""
"— Nessun ostacolo, ma i giocatori possono avanzare orizzontalmente nella "
"loro metà"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:117
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— No timer, first to 5 goals, puck speeds up with each goal"
msgstr "— Nessun timer, prima a 5 gol, puck accelera con ogni obiettivo"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_blizzard.html.heex:48
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Not all ice rows are equal. Focus on rows with predictable patterns first."
msgstr ""
"— Non tutte le file di ghiaccio sono uguali. Focus sulle righe con modelli "
"prevedibili prima."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_stagecoach.html.heex:66
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— One bullet at a time. A wasted shot on the stagecoach gives your opponent "
"a free window to reposition."
msgstr ""
"— Un proiettile alla volta. Un colpo sprecato sul pallone da palcoscenico dà"
" al tuo avversario una finestra libera per riposizionare."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:86
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Open/close on blocks. Open = dangerous, closed = safe (from round 4)"
msgstr "— Aprire i blocchi. Aperto = pericoloso, chiuso = sicuro (da tondo 4)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:68
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Patrols the shore. Dodge to reach your igloo!"
msgstr "— Patrols la riva. Dodge per raggiungere il tuo igloo!"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_peaceful.html.heex:55
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Perfect your jump timing between rows to minimize time between block "
"collections."
msgstr ""
"— Perfetto il tempo di salto tra le righe per minimizzare il tempo tra le "
"collezioni di blocchi."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:44
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Puck reflects off top/bottom walls"
msgstr "— Puck si riflette sulle pareti di alto livello"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_boxing.html.heex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Punch (alternates left/right arm automatically)"
msgstr "— Punch (alterna automaticamente il braccio a sinistra"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:74
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Ride the ice blocks (from round 2)"
msgstr "— Guidare i blocchi di ghiaccio (da tondo 2)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_sudden.html.heex:51
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Risky shots that go out cost you a whole game. Consistency beats flash in "
"Sudden Death."
msgstr ""
"— Risky colpi che escono costano un intero gioco. La costanza batte il flash"
" nella morte improvvisa."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_night.html.heex:69
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Save your turbo boost for fog-free moments when you can actually see the "
"road."
msgstr ""
"— Risparmia la tua spinta turbo per i momenti senza nebbia quando si può "
"effettivamente vedere la strada."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_blitz.html.heex:50
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Scarce fuel means every depot matters. Plan your path to hit fuel depots "
"even if it means fewer enemy kills."
msgstr ""
"— Il combustibile scarso significa ogni deposito. Pianifica il tuo percorso "
"per colpire depositi di carburante anche se significa meno nemici uccide."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_quick.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_sudden.html.heex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Serve (during serving phase)"
msgstr "— Serve (durante la fase di servizio)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_sudden.html.heex:58
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Server alternates after every point. Know when you're serving to maximize "
"advantage."
msgstr ""
"— Il server si alterna dopo ogni punto. Sapere quando si sta servendo per "
"massimizzare il vantaggio."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders.html.heex:68
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Shared screen, no alien drops, fight together"
msgstr "— Schermo condiviso, nessuna goccia aliena, combattere insieme"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_clean.html.heex:38
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Sharp turns slow you down. Plan your path 2-3 obstacles ahead for the "
"smoothest line."
msgstr ""
"- Sharp ti rallenta. Pianifica il tuo percorso 2-3 ostacoli avanti per la "
"linea più liscia."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Shoot in your facing direction"
msgstr "— Spara nella tua direzione di fronte"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_pacifist.html.heex:52
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Slow down for dense enemy clusters to maximize hits. Speed up in empty "
"stretches to save fuel."
msgstr ""
"— Rallentare per cluster nemici densi per massimizzare i colpi. Accelerare "
"in tratti vuoti per risparmiare carburante."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing.html.heex:54
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Sparse obstacles, slow avalanche, wide gates"
msgstr "— Distruggi ostacoli, valanga lenta, porte larghe"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_escape.html.heex:50
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Speed boosts keep you ahead of the avalanche. Missing one could be fatal "
"later."
msgstr ""
"— La velocità aumenta la tenuta davanti alla valanga. La scomparsa potrebbe "
"essere fatale dopo."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:69
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Standard 60% success rate. Don't commit to a tackle unless you're sure "
"you're close enough."
msgstr ""
"— tasso di successo standard del 60%. Non impegnarti ad affrontare se non "
"sei sicuro di essere abbastanza vicino."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_ricochet.html.heex:65
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Standing near the ceiling or floor gives your bullets a shorter bounce "
"path, making them harder to dodge."
msgstr ""
"— In piedi vicino al soffitto o al pavimento dà ai proiettili un percorso di"
" rimbalzo più breve, rendendoli più difficili da schivare."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_blitz.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_pacifist.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Steer jet laterally"
msgstr "— Molo di scarico in seguito"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_clean.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_escape.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Steer left/right"
msgstr "— Steer sinistra"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:38
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Step on your own block to undo it (-1 piece)"
msgstr "— Passo sul proprio blocco per annullarlo (-1 pezzo)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:45
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Step to steal it! You +1 piece, they -1 piece (2-piece swing!)"
msgstr "- Passo a rubarlo! +1 pezzo, -1 pezzo (2 pezzi swing!)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_blizzard.html.heex:55
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Stepping on your opponent's blocks steals them. Use it offensively when "
"you're ahead."
msgstr ""
"— Passeggiare sui blocchi del tuo avversario li ruba. Usalo in modo "
"offensivo quando sei avanti."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:23
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:23
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:23
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Tackle opponent to steal puck"
msgstr "— avversario tackle per rubare puck"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:69
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— The 25% speed boost makes long-range shots more effective. Catch the "
"opponent off guard."
msgstr ""
"— L'aumento della velocità del 25% rende i colpi a lungo raggio più "
"efficaci. Prendere l'avversario di guardia."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:62
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— The 80% success rate means tackling is almost always worth it. Chase the "
"puck carrier relentlessly."
msgstr ""
"— Il tasso di successo dell'80% significa affrontare è quasi sempre ne vale "
"la pena. Insegui il portapacchi senza sosta."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_quick.html.heex:60
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— The ball angle depends on where it hits your player. Position yourself to "
"control shot direction."
msgstr ""
"— L'angolo della palla dipende da dove colpisce il giocatore. Posizionati a "
"controllare la direzione del tiro."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_escape.html.heex:43
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— The center of the course gives you the most options to dodge left or right"
" as obstacles appear."
msgstr ""
"— Il centro del corso ti dà la maggior parte delle opzioni per schivare a "
"sinistra o a destra come appaiono gli ostacoli."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:55
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— The first few goals are at normal puck speed. Build a lead before the puck"
" becomes a missile."
msgstr ""
"— I primi obiettivi sono alla velocità normale del puck. Costruire una pista"
" prima che il puck diventi un missile."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_stagecoach.html.heex:45
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— The stagecoach bounces at a constant speed. Count the timing and fire "
"during the gap windows."
msgstr ""
"— La cannocchiaia rimbalza a velocità costante. Contare i tempi e il fuoco "
"durante le finestre del vuoto."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_stagecoach.html.heex:52
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— The stagecoach spends the least time at the top and bottom of its bounce, "
"creating wider shooting windows."
msgstr ""
"— La plancia spende meno tempo in cima e in basso del suo rimbalzo, creando "
"più ampie finestre di tiro."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_clean.html.heex:52
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Tight gaps require micro-adjustments. Don't overcorrect and bounce between"
" obstacles."
msgstr ""
"— Le lacune strette richiedono micro-aggiustamenti. Non esagerare e "
"rimbalzare tra gli ostacoli."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_pacifist.html.heex:59
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Touching the riverbank kills you instantly. Stay centered when the river "
"narrows."
msgstr ""
"- Toccare la riva del fiume ti uccide istantaneamente. Restate in centro "
"quando il fiume si restringe."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:32
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Walk into the free puck to pick it up automatically"
msgstr "— Camminare nel puck libero per prenderlo automaticamente"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_sprint.html.heex:65
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Weave through tight gaps between AI cars. Each overtake counts — even "
"risky ones."
msgstr ""
"— Sfruttate le strette lacune tra le automobili dell'AI. Ogni "
"sovrapposizione conta - anche quelli rischiosi."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:62
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— When the puck is fast, stay between the puck and your goal. Reaction time "
"shrinks."
msgstr ""
"— Quando il puck è veloce, rimanere tra il puck e il vostro obiettivo. Il "
"tempo di reazione si restringe."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_blizzard.html.heex:41
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— With 60° on the clock, you have time. Don't rush jumps and fall into the "
"water."
msgstr ""
"— Con 60° sull'orologio, avete tempo. Non saltare di fretta e cadere "
"nell'acqua."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:55
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— With 80% tackle success, holding the puck is dangerous. Shoot on sight."
msgstr ""
"— Con l'80% di affrontare il successo, tenere il puck è pericoloso. Spara a "
"vista."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_blitz.html.heex:43
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— With a 3-second cooldown, you can drop mines much more frequently. Use "
"them to disrupt your opponent's rhythm."
msgstr ""
"— Con un raffreddore di 3 secondi, si può cadere mine molto più "
"frequentemente. Usali per interrompere il ritmo del tuo avversario."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_sprint.html.heex:58
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— With clear visibility, use turbo when the road ahead is clear for maximum "
"overtakes."
msgstr ""
"— Con una chiara visibilità, utilizzare turbo quando la strada avanti è "
"chiara per il massimo superamento."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_blitz.html.heex:44
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— With lowered combo thresholds (2 kills for a drop), rapid-fire is your "
"best weapon against the opponent."
msgstr ""
"— Con soglie combinate abbassate (2 uccisioni per una goccia), il fuoco "
"rapido è la vostra arma migliore contro l'avversario."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_nml.html.heex:57
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— With no obstacles, vertical movement is your only defense. Never stand "
"still."
msgstr ""
"— Senza ostacoli, il movimento verticale è la vostra unica difesa. Mai stare"
" fermo."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_sudden.html.heex:44
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— With one-point games, an ace or unreturnable serve is an instant game win."
msgstr ""
"— Con giochi di un punto, un asso o un servizio invertibile è una vittoria "
"di gioco istantaneo."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_quick.html.heex:39
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— With only 3 games needed, losing even one game puts you at a serious "
"disadvantage."
msgstr ""
"— Con solo 3 giochi necessari, perdendo anche un gioco ti mette a uno "
"svantaggio serio."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_blitz.html.heex:64
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— With only 5 sections, maximizing points per section is key. Prioritize "
"high-value targets."
msgstr ""
"— Con solo 5 sezioni, massimizzare i punti per sezione è fondamentale. "
"Priorizzare obiettivi di alto valore."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_peaceful.html.heex:41
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Without block stealing, the fastest path through the ice rows wins. Plan "
"your circuit."
msgstr ""
"— Senza il blocco di rubare, il percorso più veloce attraverso le file di "
"ghiaccio vince. Pianifica il tuo circuito."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_pacifist.html.heex:45
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"— Without mines to worry about, you can fly more aggressively. But don't "
"forget to refuel — fuel depots are your lifeline."
msgstr ""
"— Senza mine di cui preoccuparsi, si può volare più aggressivo. Ma non "
